data.description: Spring Mountain Ranch in Riverside County offers miles of walking trails surrounded by mountains.  Just listed for sale:  21132 Bison Mesa Road a single story home with 4 bedrooms and 2 full baths on a 9000 square foot lot. The backyard features an in ground pool, jacuzzi and concrete decking, the work  was completed in 2023. Enjoy it year round!
